{"tid":1614751,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又話香港人適應力強既？","createTime":"2019-10-03T01:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T01:42:43.000Z","uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1ca0269d7375159c0595a5fe1fce04ec9d3060","tid":1614751,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"爆佢兩間鋪就嘈住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呀！<br />\n乜都嘢叫適應力呀！<br />\n<br />\n你食開清湯<br />\n可唔可以一下變食特辣呀<br />\n<br />\n革命係以年計<br />\n我地可以慢慢升級<br />\n<br />\n火魔法一開始都好驚啦<br />\n依架咪變咗點解咁都未燒中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以爆鋪一定要做好文宣！<br />\n暫時目標只有<br />\n1.去過聯合國抹黑香港人既美心<br />\n2.斬到手足無咗隻腳既福建幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵唔算爆鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就係政府部門<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做好文宣！<br />\n目標明確！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c278cea061a9e1259c85d742aff696014de1860","tid":1614751,"uid":272976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"係好撚強呀，前日學生食子彈，尋日照常返工<br />\n利申尋日有罷"},{"pid":"3175ab876276bfacb5009eae84eefa70b476d5e6","tid":1614751,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:42:43.000Z","msg":"做文宣！"}]}